T02TD3614E:238a-4: dpal ldan dzam bha la la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3614E:238a-5: sngon ma bzhin du stong pa nyid kyi mthar thug pa rnam par bsams nas /
T02TD3614E:238a-6: sna tshogs padma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i steng du zla ba la dzam yig las skyes pa'i bcom ldan 'das dzam bha la bsgom par bya ste /
T02TD3614E:238a-7: gser gyi mdog can lta bu thung zhing lto ba 'phyad ba /
T02TD3614E:238a-8: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3614E:238b-0: g-yon pa dang g-yas pa'i phyag @238b dag gis /
T02TD3614E:238b-1: sre mo dang b'i dza p'u ra ka bsnams pa /
T02TD3614E:238b-2: rin chen 'byung ldan gyis dbu brgyan pa /
T02TD3614E:238b-3: autpa la'i phreng ba bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3614E:238b-4: shar la sogs pa'i 'dab ma rnams su nor bu bzang po dang gang ba bzang po dang /
T02TD3614E:238b-5: nor sbyin dang rnam thos sras rnams so //
T02TD3614E:238b-6: me la sogs pa'i 'dab ma la ki li mi li dang /
T02TD3614E:238b-10: de bzhin du ji ltar gsungs pa'i rim pas nor rgyun ma dang /
T02TD3614E:238b-18: gnod sbyin mo 'di rnams bsam par bya'o //
T02TD3614E:238b-19: nor rgyun ma ni dzam bha la dang lhan cig tu'o //
T02TD3614E:238b-20: gnod sbyin mo rnams ni nor rgyun ma ji lta ba bzhin no //
T02TD3614E:238b-21: gnod sbyin rnams dzam bha la bzhin te /
T02TD3614E:238b-22: de bzhin du bsams nas sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD3614E:238b-23: de la gnod sbyin rnams kyi sngags ni /
T02TD3614E:238b-24: aom dzam bha la dza lendra ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-25: aom ma ni bha dra ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-26: aom purna bha dra ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-27: aom dha na d'a ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-28: aom bee shra ma n'a yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-29: aom ki li mi ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-30: aom tsi bi kunda li yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-31: aom mu khendra ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-32: aom tsa re ndra ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-33: de nas gnod sbyin mo rnams kyi sngags ni /
T02TD3614E:238b-34: aom ba su dha r'a ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-35: aom tsandra kanta yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-36: aom dha na d'a yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-37: so su danta yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-38: aom a'a ry'a yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-39: aom su bha dr'a yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-40: aom gu pa ta yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-41: aom de b'i yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-42: aom sva ra sva t'i yee sv'a h'a /
T02TD3614E:238b-43: de bzhin du thun mtshams gsum du bsgoms nas /
T02TD3614E:238b-44: chu khyor ba brgya rtsa brgyad rab tu phul bas /
T02TD3614E:238b-45: 'jig rten gsum gyi mnga' ris ster bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD3614E:238b-46: snga bar bya rog mi grag pa tsam na chu'i nang du bzlas na nor mi nyams shing 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD3614E:238b-47: de nas gser la sogs pa'i snod du nor rgyun ma dang gnod sbyin lhan cig tu'o //
T02TD3614E:238b-48: snod gnyis par bcom ldan 'das dzambha la gnod sbyin gyis yongs su bskor ba bris te yang dag par sbyar nas bsgrub par bya'o //
T02TD3614E:238b-49: dngos grub chen po brgyad la sogs pa yang ster bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD3614E:238b-50: dzambha la'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
